<br>
&quot;That's my girl!&quot;<br>
<br>
She shouted aloud and then turned back into the village looking for any women.<br>
A small group of women peeked out of one of the tents and looked at their &quot;husbands&quot; lying dead in the village. They all looked up at the amazons going back into the forests.<br>
<br>
One of the women looked up at the others.<br>
&quot;What are we waiting for? Let's leave!&quot; She cried.<br>
The other women stood back afraid of leaving all they knew.<br>
